<br>
Aary &amp; all other NToV mobs are on 7 day timer.  Aary is insta pop on server up.  All others spawn within 1-24 hours of server up.  Due to the layout of NToV, you can be in there for hours clearing everything &amp; killing.  *shrug*<br>
<br>
The &quot;no killing&quot; part basically starts when Aary up/due up.  Work with the guild before you in rotation, and get the time of death, shouldn't be real tough.  You don't even need an SoS rogue to see Aary, a non KOS druid can track from safe hall, anyone non KOS with an eye (even stalking probe) can run an eye into Aary pit from door before entering NToV (yes, the one before safe hall).  So a wizard, mage, bard, warrior, paladin, anyone can track, either have the eye spell, or hit bazaar &amp; pick up a stalking probe or two to keep an eye on pit.<br>
<br>
