Last time Isen was in NToV (Week of July 1),  we had Ikitar, Aary, Fesh, Dagarn and Kreizzen up on Tuesday, Wednesday had Koi'dokken and Mir, Thursday had Triplets, then Sunday (Which we left NToV due to the Holiday weekend), Vyemm and Nev spawned.  Thank god there was a patch to un-fubar the spawns.<br>
